cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically single-image haze removal. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests it could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with color priors and ambient illumination, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
